meta.commit_message:
scan errors and warnings (#3175)

* scan errors now appear after each point instead of at end of whole scan

* remove unit test for show_errors since it has been removed from SingleRun

* Add line of asterisks and blank line to terminal output between scan points

* Add scan convergence summary with convergence percentage

* format outputs to have the same indentation

* Converged percentage to 2dp

* align the converged/unconverged column

* Add blank line after Scan Convergence Summary and the first scan point result

* show errors for once through runs

* Update process/main.py
